{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":360,"text":"In the last couple of years,"},{"time":2160,"text":"I have produced what I call\n\"The Dead Mall Series,\""},{"time":4920,"text":"32 short films and counting\nabout dead malls."},{"time":7200,"text":"Now, for those of you who are\nnot familiar with what a dead mall is,"},{"time":11640,"text":"it's basically a shopping mall"},{"time":14080,"text":"that has fallen into hard times."},{"time":17200,"text":"So it either has few shops\nand fewer shoppers,"},{"time":20000,"text":"or it's abandoned and crumbling into ruin."},{"time":25280,"text":"No sale at Penny's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28360,"text":"I started producing this series"},{"time":30760,"text":"in early 2015"},{"time":33640,"text":"after going through\nkind of a dark period in my life"},{"time":36120,"text":"where I just didn't want\nto create films anymore."},{"time":39640,"text":"I put my camera away"},{"time":41600,"text":"and I just stopped."},{"time":44880,"text":"So in 2015, I decided to make\na short film about the Owings Mills Mall."},{"time":51480,"text":"Owings Mills Mall opened in 1986."},{"time":54600,"text":"I should know because\nI was there on opening day."},{"time":58560,"text":"I was there with my family,"},{"time":59920,"text":"along with every other\nfamily in Baltimore,"},{"time":64000,"text":"and you had to drive around"},{"time":65680,"text":"for 45 minutes"},{"time":67400,"text":"just to find a parking spot."},{"time":69200,"text":"So if you can imagine,"},{"time":70760,"text":"that's not happening at the malls today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73480,"text":"My first mall job that I had as a teenager"},{"time":76840,"text":"was at a sporting goods store\ncalled Herman's World of Sports."},{"time":81400,"text":"Maybe you remember."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82640,"text":"(Singing) Herman's World of Sports."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84560,"text":"You guys remember that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87080,"text":"Yeah, so I worked in a lady's shoe store."},{"time":92400,"text":"I worked in a leather goods store,"},{"time":94920,"text":"and I also worked in a video store,"},{"time":100120,"text":"and not being one who was\nvery fond of the retail arts --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109560,"text":"I got fired from every single job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":114280,"text":"In between these low-paying retail jobs,"},{"time":119480,"text":"I did what any normal teenager did"},{"time":122240,"text":"in the 1990s."},{"time":124920,"text":"I shoplifted."},{"time":128080,"text":"I'm just kidding."},{"time":129320,"text":"I hung out with my friends at the mall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132800,"text":"Everyone's like, \"Oh my God,\nwhat kind of talk is this?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":136840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141080,"text":"Hanging out at the mall could be fun,\nbut it could be really lame, too,"},{"time":144440,"text":"like sharing a cigarette\nwith a 40-year-old unemployed mall rat"},{"time":149920,"text":"who has put on\nblack lipstick for the night"},{"time":153080,"text":"while you're on your break\nfrom your crappy minimum wage job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160480,"text":"As I stand here today,"},{"time":163120,"text":"Owings Mills has been gutted"},{"time":166040,"text":"and it's ready for the wrecking ball."},{"time":170480,"text":"The last time I was there,\nit was in the evening,"},{"time":173160,"text":"and it was about three days\nbefore they closed the mall for good."},{"time":178720,"text":"And you kind of felt --"},{"time":180120,"text":"they never announced the mall was closing,"},{"time":182160,"text":"but you had this sort of feeling,\nthis ominous feeling,"},{"time":184800,"text":"that something big was going to happen,"},{"time":187600,"text":"like it was the end of the road."},{"time":190160,"text":"It was a very creepy walk\nthrough the mall."},{"time":193720,"text":"Let me show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202600,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"So when I started producing\n\"The Dead Mall Series,\""},{"time":229440,"text":"I put the videos up onto YouTube,"},{"time":231200,"text":"and while I thought they were interesting,"},{"time":233360,"text":"frankly I didn't think others\nwould share the enthusiasm"},{"time":237960,"text":"for such a drab and depressing topic."},{"time":242280,"text":"But apparently I was wrong,"},{"time":243640,"text":"because a lot of people\nstarted to comment."},{"time":245720,"text":"And at first the comments were like --"},{"time":249160,"text":"basically like, \"Oh my God,\nthat's the mall from my childhood."},{"time":252520,"text":"What happened?\""},{"time":254480,"text":"And then I would get comments\nfrom people who were like,"},{"time":257880,"text":"\"There's a dead mall in my town.\nYou should come and film it.\""},{"time":261279,"text":"So I started to travel around\nthe mid-Atlantic region"},{"time":266080,"text":"filming these dead malls."},{"time":268720,"text":"Some were open."},{"time":270840,"text":"Some were abandoned."},{"time":272920,"text":"It was kind of always hard\nto get into the ones that were abandoned,"},{"time":276560,"text":"but I somehow always found a way in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281480,"text":"The malls that are still open,"},{"time":285560,"text":"they always do this weird thing --\nlike the dead malls."},{"time":288200,"text":"They'll have three stores left,"},{"time":289760,"text":"but they try to spruce it up"},{"time":291800,"text":"to make it appear\nlike things are on the up-and-up."},{"time":295160,"text":"For example,"},{"time":297040,"text":"you'll have an empty store"},{"time":299080,"text":"and they bring the gate down."},{"time":300880,"text":"So at Owings Mills, for example,\nthey put this tarp over the gate."},{"time":305080,"text":"Right?"},{"time":306360,"text":"And it's got a stock photo"},{"time":309960,"text":"of a woman who is so happy"},{"time":312640,"text":"and she's holding a blouse,"},{"time":314280,"text":"and she's like --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319120,"text":"And then there's a guy\nstanding next to her, with, like,"},{"time":321800,"text":"an espresso cup, and he's like --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":324080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326880,"text":"And it says, \"What brings you today?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":331240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":332560,"text":"I wanted to be scared and depressed."},{"time":335760,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339960,"text":"So the comments just kept pouring in"},{"time":344360,"text":"on the videos,"},{"time":346320,"text":"from all over the country,\nand then all over the world."},{"time":351000,"text":"And I started to think,\nthis could really be something,"},{"time":353640,"text":"but I had to get creative,\nbecause I'm like,"},{"time":355960,"text":"how long are people going to sit and watch\nme waddling through an empty mall?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365400,"text":"So the original episodes\nI filmed with an iPhone."},{"time":369680,"text":"So I'd walk through the mall\nwith an iPhone, and, you know."},{"time":373960,"text":"Like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376680,"text":"And security -- because malls,\nthey don't like photography --"},{"time":380520,"text":"so the security would come up and be like,\n\"Put that away,\" and I'm like, \"OK.\""},{"time":384280,"text":"So I had to get creative and sneaky,"},{"time":386640,"text":"so I started using a hidden camera\nand different techniques"},{"time":390240,"text":"to get the footage that I needed,"},{"time":391880,"text":"and basically what I wanted to do"},{"time":394040,"text":"was make the video"},{"time":396280,"text":"like it was a first-person experience,"},{"time":398640,"text":"like you are sitting --"},{"time":402600,"text":"put your headphones on\nwatching the screen --"},{"time":404760,"text":"it's like, you're there in the video,"},{"time":406680,"text":"like a video game, basically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410520,"text":"I also started to use music,"},{"time":413000,"text":"collaborating with artists\nwho create music called vaporwave."},{"time":416280,"text":"And vaporwave is a music genre"},{"time":419240,"text":"that emerged in the early 2010s\namong internet communities."},{"time":423240,"text":"Here's an example."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424560,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":456840,"text":"That's by an artist named Disconscious"},{"time":460000,"text":"from an album he did\ncalled \"Hologram Plaza.\""},{"time":462200,"text":"So if you look that up,\nyou can hear more of those tunes."},{"time":465880,"text":"Vaporwave is more than an art form.\nIt's like a movement."},{"time":469720,"text":"It's nihilistic, it's angsty,"},{"time":472680,"text":"but it's somehow comforting."},{"time":474880,"text":"The whole aesthetic is a way of dealing\nwith things you can't do anything about,"},{"time":480120,"text":"like no jobs, or sitting in your parents'\nbasement eating ramen noodles."},{"time":485280,"text":"Vaporwave came out of this generation's\ndesire to express their hopelessness,"},{"time":489480,"text":"the same way that\nthe pre-internet generation did"},{"time":493240,"text":"sitting around in the food court."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497280,"text":"One of my favorite malls"},{"time":500760,"text":"I've been to"},{"time":502840,"text":"is in Corpus Christi,\nand it's called the Sunrise Mall."},{"time":506640,"text":"When I was a kid,"},{"time":508480,"text":"my favorite thing to do was watch movies,"},{"time":510560,"text":"and I used to watch movies\nover and over and over again."},{"time":513520,"text":"And one of my favorite films\nwas \"The Legend of Billie Jean.\""},{"time":519360,"text":"Now, for those of you who have seen\n\"The Legend of Billie Jean,\""},{"time":522400,"text":"you'll know that it's a great film."},{"time":525760,"text":"I love it."},{"time":527000,"text":"And Helen Slater and Christian Slater --"},{"time":528929,"text":"and if you didn't know,\nthey are not related."},{"time":531080,"text":"Many people thought that they\nwere brother and sister. They're not."},{"time":534280,"text":"But anyway, Sunrise Mall was used\nin the film as a filming location."},{"time":537680,"text":"The mall is exactly the same\nas it was in 1984."},{"time":543240,"text":"We're talking 32 years later.\nLet me show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546000,"text":"(Video) Dan Bell: And here's Billie Jean\nrunning across the fountain,"},{"time":550520,"text":"being chased by Hubie Pyatt's friends."},{"time":554840,"text":"And she jumps over here."},{"time":559360,"text":"And you can see the shot right here\nis what it looks like today."},{"time":565760,"text":"It's pretty incredible."},{"time":567040,"text":"I mean, honestly, it's exactly the same."},{"time":571400,"text":"And there they are\nfalling in the fountain,"},{"time":573440,"text":"and she runs up the stairs."},{"time":574800,"text":"This is a nice shot\nof the whole thing here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581549,"text":"Dan Bell: I love that so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585440,"text":"I always think in my head,\nif I owned a dead mall --"},{"time":589760,"text":"why don't they embrace their vintage look?"},{"time":592440,"text":"Put in a bar,"},{"time":594840,"text":"like, put vegan food in the food court"},{"time":599960,"text":"and invite millennials and hipsters"},{"time":603080,"text":"to come and drink and eat,"},{"time":605880,"text":"and I guarantee you within three weeks"},{"time":607840,"text":"H&amp;M and Levi's will be banging\non the door trying to get space."},{"time":612000,"text":"I don't know why they don't do this,"},{"time":613760,"text":"but apparently,"},{"time":615160,"text":"it's only in my mind, it goes all day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":622080,"text":"Anyway, in closing --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":623320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":627360,"text":"When they first asked me to do this talk,"},{"time":630640,"text":"I said,"},{"time":632640,"text":"\"Do you have the right person?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":634160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":639080,"text":"These talks are supposed\nto be kind of inspiring and --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":642320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648480,"text":"I remembered something, though."},{"time":650440,"text":"I put my camera down\nthree or four years ago,"},{"time":656680,"text":"and it took going to these malls"},{"time":660480,"text":"for me to be inspired again."},{"time":664080,"text":"And to see my audience"},{"time":667320,"text":"and people from all over the world\nwriting me and saying,"},{"time":670240,"text":"\"God, I love your videos,\""},{"time":672480,"text":"is incredible."},{"time":675200,"text":"I don't know how to even explain it,"},{"time":677000,"text":"as an artist,"},{"time":678400,"text":"how fulfilling that is."},{"time":680320,"text":"If you would have told me a year ago"},{"time":683600,"text":"that I would be standing on this stage"},{"time":686440,"text":"talking to all of you wonderful people,"},{"time":689360,"text":"I would have never believed it."},{"time":690880,"text":"I am humbled"},{"time":692320,"text":"and so appreciative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694160,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695400,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}